snippet.title: World of Final Fantasy - Tokyo Game Show Trailer 2016
snippet.description:
Watch the latest trailer for World of Final Fantasy as shown during Tokyo Game Show 2016.  

Follow the journey of siblings, Reynn and Lann, as they enter the world of Grymoire and encounter a multitude of familiar FINAL FANTASY® characters and creatures. WORLD OF FINAL FANTASY® is coming to PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita on October 28th 2016 in Europe and October 25th 2016 in North America.

Limited Edition: http://bit.ly/2eoR9rg
Day 1 Edition-: http://bit.ly/2bY4rGu
